  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Advocating for innocent woman &amp; children in prison</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">There are over 5,000 Nigerian women in diaspora prisons; these women are facing police brutality, rape, pregnancy, death and are sold into prostitution. ECF is yearning to rescue these women and the children born as a result of rape. Also, many women have spent years awaiting trial in Nigerian prison because they cannot afford legal representation; after a thorough research by our legal team, it was discovered that 92% of these women are innocent. Let&apos;s put an end to these together.</narrative>
  </description>
